[assistant] Key changes:
[assistant] - Removed direct private serialization-hook invocation via `MethodHandles`.
[assistant] - Kept coverage focused on `ProvDSTU4145PrivateKey`.
[assistant] - Added a nested-holder serialization test to exercise the key when serialized as a field of another serializable object.
