[assistant]   - `ObjectOutputStream.writeObject(...)`
[assistant]   - `ObjectOutputStream.writeUnshared(...)`
[assistant]   - `ObjectInputStream.readObject()`
[assistant]   - `ObjectInputStream.readUnshared()`
